{"titles": {"CN": "冬日攻势", "EN": "Winter Offensive", "JP": "夏(?)の大作戦", "KR": "여름(?)의 대작전", "TW": "冬日攻勢"}, "regions": {"CN": {"冬天与被炉": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">一　冬天与被炉</span><br>"]}, {"say": "呼…果然冬天还是最适合被炉呢…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "哈啊…感觉要和被炉融为一体了…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "唉…看你这样子…真是不成体统…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "哎～姐姐自己还不是一样窝在被炉里～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "咳咳…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "没办法嘛…谁让冬天这么冷呢～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "再这样下去，身体都要变差了呢，冬天也需要锻炼身体呀", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "诶～这种天气？能做什么锻炼嘛……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "比如…冬泳什么的？还能锻炼气魄呢？嘻嘻…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "咿～这玩笑一点都不好笑啦…想想都觉得好冷呀…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "冬泳大会？": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">二　冬泳大会？</span><br>"]}, {"say": "哈…哈啾！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "呜…果然好冷啊外面…咦？前面的是？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "哟！这不是山城吗，出来散步吗？", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "没有啦…只是出来买点东西，呜…好冷……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不行啊山城～作为重樱的一员，怎么能被区区冷空气打倒呢！", "actorName": "伊势", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "日向、伊势…你们都好厉害啊～不觉得冷吗？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "哼哼，寒冷这种东西，靠气势就能赶跑啦！", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "我们还准备办个冬泳大会呢！哼哼，把白鹰那些家伙们也叫上，让她们见识一下重樱的气魄！", "actorName": "伊势", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "怎么样？山城你也要一起参加吗？", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "呜…我就……算了…哈…哈啾！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "遗失的礼物·上": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">三 遗失的礼物·上</span><br>"]}, {"say": "冬泳…冬泳吗…虽然说作为巫女…在冬天也会有需要用冰冷的清水洁净身躯的时候……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "似乎最近…确实有些怠惰了呢……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "夏天时候的泳装…指挥官送的…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "我记得是收在这里了……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "咦？怎么找不到了？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "遗失的礼物·下": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">四 遗失的礼物·下</span><br>"]}, {"say": "呜呜…到底哪里去了…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "嗯？你在找什么呢？翻箱倒柜的", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "呜呜…指挥官送的泳装…找不到了啦……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "唉，傻瓜，不是你说的是指挥官送的非常重要的东西，所以就特意另外找了个柜子收起来了吗？", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "这里，找到啦", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "哇！谢谢姐姐呜呜…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "怎么突然想起找泳装了…该不会…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "真的想冬泳了吧～？", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "之前出门遇到了日向她们，总觉得作为重樱的一员…不能这么堕落下去了", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "哎呀呀，山城真是个好孩子呢～", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不如去问问指挥官要不要一起锻炼？", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "姐、姐姐！又开我玩笑…而且指挥官那么忙…怎么会有时间……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "邀请": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">五 邀请</span><br>"]}, {"say": "殿、殿下！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "…？", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "一、一起去游泳吧！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……？！", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "其实是……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "所以…要一起去锻炼一下气魄吗！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "不、不行？难得把殿下送的泳装都拿出来了……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "！（点头）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "可以吗？！诶嘿嘿…那就去日向他们开游泳大会的地方看看吧～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "耐寒大会？": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">六 耐寒大会？</span><br>"]}, {"say": "怎怎怎怎么样！见识到重樱的气魄了吗！", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "喝！只只只只要气势足够，寒、寒冷什么的，都不在、在话下！", "actorName": "伊势", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "努噢噢哦噢噢！这次在下绝对不会输给你了！萨拉托加小姐！！", "actorName": "高雄", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "呜呜呜呜呜…为为为什么萨拉托加要来参加这种惩罚游戏一样的比赛啦！！", "actor": 107031, "actorName": "萨拉托加 [七海的憩日]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "看上去…很冷呢…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "果、果然还是换个锻炼方式吧？看上去对健康并不怎么好呢，殿下？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……（点头）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "温泉Attack!": [{"sequence": ["冬日攻势&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">七 温泉Attack!</span><br>"]}, {"say": "呼哈～～复活了复活了～～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "嘻嘻，果然冬天还是更适合温泉呢～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "锻、锻炼？那种事还是等到夏天再……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "还是说…殿、殿下不喜欢和我一起泡温泉呢？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "！！（摇头）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "嘿嘿…殿下送的泳装，山城一直很珍惜地收着唷～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "虽然还有很多辛苦的事、让人难过的事…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "但是只要能和大家、和殿下像这样在一起…就感觉什么都不是问题了呢！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "从今往后也请多多关照了哦？殿～下～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "EN": {"Winter and Kotatsu": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 1 - A Kotatsu in the Winter</span><br>"]}, {"say": "Phew... there's nothing quite like a warm kotatsu during the winter...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ahh... I don't want to ever get out...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "My, my, is that how you should be acting?", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ehh? But Fusou, you look pretty cozy too...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Umm... *cough*", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "It's not like I have a choice... it's way too cold this year...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "We're going to get all chubby at this rate. Even if it's cold, we're going to need to get some exercise.", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ehh? In this weather? What kind of stuff is there to do?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hmm... how about cold-water freediving? We'd also be able to show some guts in the process. Heehee~", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Jeez, Fusou, don't even make jokes about that... just thinking about it is making me cold...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Winter Swimming Competition?": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 2 - Cold-Water Swim Meet?</span><br>"]}, {"say": "Aah... Aachoo!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ughh... I knew it'd be freezing outside... Huh? Who's that...?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Yo, if it isn't Yamashiro! Are you out for a stroll?", "actorName": "Hyuuga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Umm... not quite... I'm just on my way to the store... Brrr...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "A poor showing, Yamashiro! How could a battleship of the Sakura Empire allow herself to be bested by a little cold?", "actorName": "Ise", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ise, Hyuuga... you two aren't cold...?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Heh. All you need is a little guts, and the cold won't be an issue at all!", "actorName": "Hyuuga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "As a matter of fact, we're organizing a cold-water swim meet. Heheh, we're also going to grab those Eagle Union blokes and let them see what the Sakura Empire is made of!", "actorName": "Ise", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "How 'bout it, Yamashiro? Want to join?", "actorName": "Hyuuga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Eep... I, um, I think I'm good... achoo!!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "The Lost gift Pt. 1": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 3 - A Lost Gift Pt. 1</span><br>"]}, {"say": "Cold-water swim meet, huh... That reminds me, I had to do a purification ritual like that last New Year's... ", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I suppose... I have been a bit lazy recently...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Milord did give me a swimsuit for the summer...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "If I remember correctly, it should be over here...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Huh? It's not here...?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "The Lost gift Pt. 2": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 4 - A Lost Gift Pt. 2</span><br>"]}, {"say": "Uuuuu... just where could it be...?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hm? Yamashiro, are you looking for something? This place is a mess.", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Fusou, I can't... find the swimsuit... that Milord gave me... waaah!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Oh, you... Didn't you keep it in a separate place because it was a special gift that you received from Commander?", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "See? It's right here.", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Yay! Thank you so much, Fusou... Uuu...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Why are you looking for your swimsuit all of a sudden? Don't tell me...", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "You're actually going to join that cold-water swim meet?", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Mm... I ran into Hyuuga outside. It made me realize that as a member of the Sakura Fleet, I can't afford to fall behind...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "My, aren't you the hard worker~", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "We don't get an opportunity like this often, so why not ask Commander to participate as well?", "actorName": "Fusou", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "D-Don't tease me like that, Fusou...! Besides, there's no way Milord will have time to spare, with all the work...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Invite": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 5 - The Invitation</span><br>"]}, {"say": "M-Milord!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hmm?", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "L-Let's go swimming together!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "What...?!", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Actually, umm...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "So that's why... we should all participate together! No guts, no glory!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Y-you don't wanna? I even took out the swimsuit that you gave me, Milord...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "*nods* ...!", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Really?! Ehehe... In that case, let's go check on Hyuuga and the others!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Cold Endurance Competiton?": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 6 - No Guts, No Glory!</span><br>"]}, {"say": "H-h-h-h-h-how's that?! Don't underestimate the S-Sakura Fleet!", "actorName": "Hyuuga", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "S-See? A-A-A-All you n-n-need is g-guts and w-winter doesn't stand a ch-chance!", "actorName": "Ise", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Nooooooo! M-Miss Saratoga! N-N-Next time, I won't lose to you again!", "actorName": "Takao", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ah... Achoo!! Wh-why did I agree to participate in this meet in this first place...? It's practically hazing!!", "actor": 107031, "actorName": "Saratoga [Seven Seas of Rest]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "You seem... pretty cold...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "M-Maybe we should find some other kind of training...? This doesn't seem very healthy. Don't you agree, Milord?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "*nods*", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Hot Spring attack!": [{"sequence": ["Winter Offensive&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 7 - Hot Springs Offensive!</span><br>"]}, {"say": "Fwaahh... I can feel my hitpoints recovering~!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Heehee, nothing beats a soak in the hot springs during the winter!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But what about training?", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "T-training? Can't that wait 'til summer...?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Milord, perhaps you don't like being in the hot springs with me?", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "That's not it!!", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Ehehe... Did you know? I've always treasured that swimsuit that you bought for me~", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "We've had to endure a whole lot of hardships up until now, and surely... more will await us in the future...", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "But as long as we're all together, we can accomplish anything!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "That's right!", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "So... please continue to guide us forward, Milord~!", "actorName": "Yamashiro", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "JP": {"冬とコタツ": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その一　冬とコタツ</span><br>"]}, {"say": "ふぅ…やっぱり冬はコタツだよね…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "はあ…もうコタツから出られないよ…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あらあら、もう行儀が悪いったら…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "えー姉さまもコタツにこもってるじゃない…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "コホンコホン…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "今年の冬は寒いし…しょうがないよね～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "このままだと体が鈍ってしまうわよ？冬も体をちゃんと鍛えないと。", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "えー外がこんなに寒いのに鍛錬なんて無理よ…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "例えば…寒中水泳とか？気合の鍛錬にもなるし？うふふ…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "もう扶桑姉さま、冗談はやめてよ…考えただけで寒くなっちゃったよぉ…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "冬季水泳大会？": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その二　冬季水泳大会？</span><br>"]}, {"say": "は…はくしょん！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "うぅ…やっぱり外は寒いよぉ…うん？あれは…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あ！山城ちゃんじゃない！散歩か？", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "えっと…ちょっと違うかな…ただの買い出しで、うぅ…寒い……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "駄目だな山城ちゃん。重桜の戦艦たる者、寒さなんかに負けてどうする！", "actorName": "伊勢", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "伊勢さん、日向さん…凄い…寒くないの？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "ふん、寒さなんぞ気合で凌いでみせる！", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "そういや、冬季水泳大会でも開こうかと考えてな。ふふん、ユニオンの奴らも誘って我が重桜の気合を見せてやる！", "actorName": "伊勢", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "どうだ？山城ちゃんも参加してみない？", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あぅ…私は……いいかな…は、はくしょん！！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "忘れた贈物・上": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その三 忘れた贈物・上</span><br>"]}, {"say": "寒中水泳…この前、正月に身体をお清めしたときは結構大変だったな……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……最近は…ちょっと怠けてるかも……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "殿様が夏に贈ってくれた水着……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "確かにここに置いてたはず……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あれ？ない……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "忘れた贈物・下": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その四 忘れた贈物・下</span><br>"]}, {"say": "あぅ…どこに置いたの…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "うん？山城、何を探しているの？こんなに散らかして。", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "姉さま…殿様が贈ってくれた水着…どこに置いたか忘れちゃったよぉ……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "もう山城ったら、殿様が贈ってくれたものは大切だからって、別の棚に置いたじゃない？", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "これね。はい。", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "わあ！姉さまありがとう…ううぅ…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "でもなんで急に水着を？もしかして…", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "伊勢たちの寒中水泳大会に参加したくなった？", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "うん…日向さんたちに会って、重桜の一員としてこのまま怠けてはいけないなぁと思って…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "あら、頑張ってるわね～", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "せっかくだから、指揮官様にも参加してもらったら？", "actorName": "扶桑", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "ね、姉さま…また山城をからかって！…殿様は忙しいからそんな時間あるわけ……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "お誘い": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その五 お誘い</span><br>"]}, {"say": "と、殿様！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "…？", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "す、水泳大会に行きませんか！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……！？", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "実は……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "だから…気合の鍛錬のために、一緒に参加してほしいです！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "だ、だめですか…せっかく殿様が贈ってくれた水着まで用意したのに……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "（ぺこり）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "いいんですか？！えへへ…じゃあ、あとで日向さんたちの所に行きましょう！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "気合で！": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その六 気合で！</span><br>"]}, {"say": "ど、どどどどうだ！？重桜の気合をみみみ見たか！", "actorName": "日向", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "くっ！ききききき気合さえあればさ、寒さなどまま、全く相手にな、ならんぞ！", "actorName": "伊勢", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "うおおおおおお！サラトガ殿！こここ、今度こそ絶対に負けないぞ！", "actorName": "高雄", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "は、はくしょん！！なな、なんでサラトガちゃんがこんな罰ゲームみたいな大会に参加しなきゃならないのー！！", "actor": 107031, "actorName": "サラトガ [大洋の休日]", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "寒そう…ですね…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "や、やっぱり別の運動にしませんか…？あまり健康にはよくなさそうですぅ…殿様？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "（ぺこり）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "温泉大作戦！": [{"sequence": ["夏（？）の大作戦&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">その七 温泉大作戦！</span><br>"]}, {"say": "ふは～生き返りました～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "えへへ、やっぱり冬は温泉ですね～", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "た、鍛錬は……また夏になるまで……", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "もしかして…殿様は山城と一緒に温泉に入りたくなかったですか？？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "！！（ぶんぶん）", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "えへへ…殿様が贈ってくれた水着、ずっと大切にしていますよ？", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "ここに来るまで、辛いことや悩んじゃったことも、たくさんあったけど…", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "みんなと、殿様と一緒なら…きっと大丈夫です！", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "…これからもよろしくお願いします♪　と・の・さ・ま♪", "actorName": "山城", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}]}, "KR": {"겨울과 코타츠": [{"sequence": ["여름(?)의 대작전&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">제1장　겨울과 코타츠</span><br>"]}, {"say": "후우… 역시 겨울엔 코타츠지…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "하아… 이제 코타츠에서 못 빠져나오겠어…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "어머 얘도 참, 버릇없게…", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "에~ 언니도 코타츠에 콕 박혀있으면서…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "엣헴 엣헴…", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "올해 겨울은 춥기도 하고… 어쩔 수 없지~", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "이대로라면 몸이 둔해진다고. 겨울에도 몸을 열심히 단련해야지.", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "에~ 바깥이 이렇게 추운데 단련이라니 무리야…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "예를 들면… 얼음물 수영이라든지? 심신단련도 될 테니, 우후훗…", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "정말이지 후소 언니, 농담은 그만둬… 생각만 했는데도 추워졌어…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}], "동계 수영 대회?": [{"sequence": ["여름(?)의 대작전&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">제2장　동계 수영 대회?</span><br>"]}, {"say": "에…엣취!", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "우으… 역시 바깥은 추워… 음? 저건…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "아! 야마시로잖아! 산책하는 건가?", "actorName": "휴가", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "그게… 산책은 아니고… 그냥 물건 사러 가는 길이야, 으으 추워……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "그럼 안 되지 야마시로쨩. 사쿠라 엠파이어의 전함이라는 자가 추위 따위에 져서 어쩌자는 거야!", "actorName": "이세", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "이세 씨, 휴가 씨… 굉장해… 안 추워?", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "흥, 추위 따위 기합으로 견뎌내 주마!", "actorName": "휴가", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "그러고 보니, 동계 수영 대회라도 열어볼까 하는데. 후훗, 이글 유니온 녀석들도 불러서 우리 사쿠라 엠파이어의 기합을 보여주겠어!", "actorName": "이세", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "어때? 야마시로도 참가해볼래?", "actorName": "휴가", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "아으… 나는…… 괜찮아… 에, 엣취!!", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}], "잊어버린 선물·상": [{"sequence": ["여름(?)의 대작전&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">제3장　잊어버린 선물·상</span><br>"]}, {"say": "얼음물 수영… 저번 정월 세신식 때는 꽤 힘들었지……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "……요즘엔... 좀 게을러졌을지도…… ", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "나리가 여름에 선물해준 수영복……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "분명 여기 놔뒀을텐데……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "어라? 없어……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}], "잊어버린 선물·하": [{"sequence": ["여름(?)의 대작전&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">제4장　잊어버린 선물·하</span><br>"]}, {"say": "아으… 어디 놔뒀지…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "응? 야마시로, 뭘 찾고 있니? 이렇게 어질러놓고선.", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "언니… 나리가 선물해준 수영복… 어디 놔뒀는지 잊어버렸어……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "……", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "야마시로도 참, 나리가 선물해준 건 소중하다며 다른 선반에 놔두지 않았니?", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "이거네, 자.", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "우아! 언니 고마워… 우으으…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "그런데 갑자기 웬 수영복? 혹시…", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "이세가 연다는 동계 수영 대회에 참가하고 싶어진 거야?", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "응… 휴가 씨 일행이랑 만나서, 사쿠라 엠파이어의 일원으로서 이렇게 게을리 있으면 안 되겠단 생각이 들어서…", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "어머, 장하네~", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "모처럼 만의 기회니 지휘관님께도 참가해보라 하는 건 어때?", "actorName": "후소", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "어, 언니… 또 야마시로를 골탕먹이려고! …나리는 바빠서 그럴 시간이 있을 리가……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}], "부탁": [{"sequence": ["여름(?)의 대작전&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">제5장　부탁</span><br>"]}, {"say": "나, 나으리이!", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "…？", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "수, 수영 대회 같이 가실래요?", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "……！？", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "실은……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "그래서… 심신단련을 위해, 함께 참가했으면 좋겠어요!", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "아, 안 될까요… 모처럼 나리가 선물해 준 수영복까지 준비했는데……", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "(끄덕)", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "괜찮나요?! 에헤헤… 그럼, 이따 휴가 씨한테 가자고요!", "actorName": "야마시로", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}], "기합으로!": [{"sequence": ["여름(?)의 대작전&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">제6장　기합으로!</span><br>"]}, {"say": "어, 어어어어어떠냐?! 사쿠라 엠파이어의 기합, 잘 보보보보았느냐!", "actorName": "휴가", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "큭! 기기기기기합만 있으면 추위 따윈 저저, 전혀 상대가 되, 되지 않는다!", "actorName": "이세", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "우오오오오오오! 새러토가 공! 이이이, 이번에야말로 절대 지지 않겠다!", "actorName": "타카오", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "에, 엣취!! 어어, 어째서 새러토가가 이런 벌칙 게임 같은 대회에 참가해야 하는 건데~!!", "actor": 107031, "actorName": "새러토가 [대양의 휴일]", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "……", "actor": 0, "actorName": "0", "nameColor": "#92fc63"}, {"say": "……